  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fcf804f4-7b56-4175-a9fa-b426a42ed9f8\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-96598e96-2367-429e-8976-debfefd1adb9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-82c99160-a16b-4de6-b1b8-46dd7c98f156\"><b>안녕하세요 사당동 한의원 이수 한의원 입니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-fcf804f4-7b56-4175-a9fa-b426a42ed9f8\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-59544fef-5a9d-4f96-8941-3ce84c65770d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"7\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_7.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5a5d129e-49a3-405c-a3c6-87e802a3829d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ab080ec8-1f37-4291-99ad-6f41657b7725\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ffdca76d-808f-43d2-ac9b-1c2aaf8ca880\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-da25c6b5-56b9-41c0-94e9-c18a2bcd9bfd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-e9782c7c-2200-44b6-9db4-151fc86371b1\"><b>겨울철 수족냉증, 단순한 추위가 아닙니다</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-76255324-504c-41fa-bdd1-6efdd39ef0d4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5cffd0a2-0212-4add-b950-bb5660bbb6ec\">겨울만 되면 손발이 얼음처럼 차갑고 시리신가요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c8c5dbc9-64ae-4b96-98f8-2e1be7e99295\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0f469bcd-5dae-4cb1-989b-de1ccb78c657\">단순히 추위를 많이 타는 것이 아니라, 혈액순환의 문제로 생기는 ‘수족냉증’일 수 있습니다. 수족냉증은 단순한 불편함을 넘어 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-03eef433-e993-4939-9774-83ea5c294ca2\"><b>피로, 관절통, 생리불순, </b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4d8356d5-53fc-4b0f-b939-d31bc5c3b9f3\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27ef92c6-b64a-4616-b76f-f19cd0e874c8\"><b>심하면 불임까지</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f4039ea6-f5ba-4a59-9feb-b62be6657404\"> 이어질 수 있는 질환이기에 조기 관리가 필요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-5a5d129e-49a3-405c-a3c6-87e802a3829d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-693908ea-aba0-433d-a807-7a5c8d649e5e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b2d40974-0e09-4a83-b616-0bc6ac2e7e2e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b2d40974-0e09-4a83-b616-0bc6ac2e7e2e\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b166fd8108bbb6d4.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1700\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1700\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b166fd8108bbb6d4.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/b166fd8108bbb6d4.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-b2d40974-0e09-4a83-b616-0bc6ac2e7e2e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-0473df99-6474-41eb-9380-6c20e1ec1ee6\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-828271aa-fcae-402e-9acc-1a716141ba1b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c5b5ebf8-514d-48e6-a8fb-b756c3242ce6\"><b>수족냉증의 주요 원인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0873f8c1-8835-4e31-9bd0-f3f558e2a06d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ddd09145-ff90-4111-ac8a-8fb6402910ee\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1af4d87b-90cb-40b9-929c-5ed0b73cf184\"><b>기혈순환 장애</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-97d909c4-e632-4a8b-a04f-4079e935253a\">: </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-952fca75-2986-4be1-91f4-bac9eb21f8bf\">한의학적으로 기(氣)와 혈(血)이 원활히 돌지 못하면 손발 끝까지 열이 전달되지 않아 차가워집니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8ee0fb53-bfa8-454d-a3f1-3c3afe52b3ba\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0eb3f32c-338d-4dfe-9214-5beb1fb0955c\"><b>호르몬 불균형</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7540909e-e66f-4c37-a708-548aa6747a0c\">:</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9757ec2e-d3df-44cb-88f3-55ad19e22d0e\"> 특히 여성은 호르몬 변화에 따라 말초혈관의 수축·이완 기능이 약해져 수족냉증이 심해질 수 있습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2ccccdda-d5f4-48d5-baf0-04b2a35f9e1a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-724ed444-7869-412a-bc40-153a715e8492\"><b>스트레스</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9ece8259-e248-40be-ae20-047e6eb97a0a\">:</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-235171db-c895-4642-808b-fba59e97cc3e\"> 긴장과 불안은 교감신경을 과도하게 자극해 혈류를 막습니다.</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7cb1f638-0803-4611-ae31-b249757bac68\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-06d8b198-e1ca-41e6-9685-0b2310c2aa00\"><b>노폐물 축적</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-fb1b6879-b4d2-45ab-ab92-8b97720cf623\">: </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d41a61a2-3427-4d12-8f6b-41c87d0ccdbf\">혈액 속 노폐물이 많으면 혈관이 좁아져 순환이 원활하지 않습니다.</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-0873f8c1-8835-4e31-9bd0-f3f558e2a06d\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-690f8d0b-e91c-488d-9145-18ce419b21b3\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-690f8d0b-e91c-488d-9145-18ce419b21b3\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/43a8ebbcd2de9e0e.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1024\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/43a8ebbcd2de9e0e.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/43a8ebbcd2de9e0e.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-690f8d0b-e91c-488d-9145-18ce419b21b3\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-67d6f9b2-f3dd-41a0-93ee-4f642013a657\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-739943a1-9caf-4d16-b0ef-c06c4a52eccf\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e438ecf5-1887-492f-a630-3d02794739e7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0eccdb02-cf7d-43cd-8f02-38b7e9be8d99\"><b>손발이 차가울 때 동반되는 증상</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f0ba2df6-003a-4a42-a3c8-aa261b9b1ed1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ac63dd9c-ec8b-4f78-89c5-4cbcd672a773\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-20c549dc-7de6-4ace-a551-4f5746ad0679\">만성 피로감</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3661080c-df68-4338-ab17-fcafbf923b82\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8162f14d-7b89-4a91-aa54-64c00e993d0b\">무릎이나 손가락의 관절통</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3bc12375-4243-4569-b67a-90f33fc46734\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-39da7901-c3bb-48c2-8843-19effd1482e9\">두통, 어지럼증</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e9811d10-53e9-482a-80e9-37f0b1eb0df1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-06cce6c6-1ef2-4576-8056-6388b8bf65b3\">여성의 경우 생리불순 및 난임 위험</span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-f0ba2df6-003a-4a42-a3c8-aa261b9b1ed1\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-095f6f95-b4f1-4639-b12c-a52fc0cea415\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-1e708190-7b13-4197-b3a0-14c7c655a9d5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n                            <blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-aa7b1f73-4f3c-4ea4-946d-91ec51ae71b5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f1ed3fa8-f328-4139-886b-81acc13967e5\"><b> 생활 속 관리와 예방법</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n                            </blockquote>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dc4a3034-2ccf-485a-9f4f-86628ae0f2a4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><ul class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-bullet-disc\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-282117e9-6f60-4ab6-b577-542012ba0400\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-172581b9-205f-4e7e-903f-b8561c3e461d\"><b>보온 습관: </b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5c2273d0-d643-4ebd-925e-b112b28aab66\"><b>얇은 옷 여러 겹, 손·발·복부를 따뜻하게 하기</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-620fda23-7ceb-4c43-9630-2f155569c1c4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a0b8f121-43f3-4c30-a72f-d937afcd40dd\"><b>따뜻한 차 마시기: 생강차, 대추차, 계피차 등은 몸속을 덥히고 혈액순환을 돕습니다.</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-908d6fc5-9ebe-4c91-a97b-318dc4d947c8\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d801f375-34ab-4a09-a05e-7a4802d3892f\"><b>가벼운 운동: 맨손 체조, 조깅, 발끝 들기 등은 말초혈액순환 개선에 효과적입니다.</b></span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-77e9710c-52e2-41ef-8533-8f1af5cd99f9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a0a7c853-f259-489b-96ce-ce82252ceb84\"><b>호흡법·명상: 스트레스를 줄이고 기혈의 흐름을 안정시키는 데 도움이 됩니다.</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cf6e023f-6f23-4d67-9841-ca2f8db5f68a\"><b>​</b></span></p></li></ul><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-dc4a3034-2ccf-485a-9f4f-86628ae0f2a4\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-5e1aa1b9-36b0-4bc9-abc9-dc1fb75ce4a0\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6bacaa72-f14a-4ee4-bad0-9cc0eda057c1\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f87065d9-18b0-4238-a337-a9264dcaad4a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4cda9624-c014-422f-b156-dc5d8b7b8f61\">수족냉증은 단순히 따뜻하게 덮는다고 해결되지 않습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bf7e6f4c-3f24-4402-9a44-e0e2cec8d1db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6a68725f-be43-466d-83f9-fa95f0ffd180\"><b>체질에 맞는 한약 처방, 침·뜸·약침 요법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-181a2821-ea20-472e-9853-4d499db7d821\"> 등을 통해 몸 전체의 순환을 개선하고, 재발하지 않도록 체질을 강화하는 것이 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-6bacaa72-f14a-4ee4-bad0-9cc0eda057c1\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-51bf737c-2718-4dfc-ad81-cd52c03f0ecb\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5b8f6044-3610-46cb-84c7-78afd3df6603\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a43dc9c0-0619-439d-8d0d-9350f870a6ea\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummyeongjo   \" id=\"SE-6cafbb9f-470b-48c6-a836-083651e9f0bf\"><i>작은 생활습관의 변화가 큰 차이를 만듭니다.</i></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bdd97952-d4e1-4f0e-a8a5-16577ce13e66\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e